<BlogPostLayout
  title="What Happened to Army of Two?"
  description="Retro commentary on EA’s Army of Two trilogy: co-op, aggro, three releases in five years, why it’s hard to play today, and what the series left behind — from the Andy’s Arcade episode."
  category="Retro"
  tags={['Army of Two']}
  publishedDate="Published on May 1, 2026"
  dateIso="2026-05-01"
